data.name: UI_LogBox.Text
data.value:
OH, COME ON!
Now this is just super embarrassing! See, in this pretty little box there was supposed to be a bunch of helpful information about the error which just occured which you could then forward onto the developer or someone who understands this kind of junk. But, instead, we actually ran into an error trying to load that information, so instead you're just stuck with these old hard-coded ramblings of a sugar-driven, sleepless developer.
*Sigh*.
